room_title: Escape room "Malus the Elf" by Locks and Puzzles Escape Room in Toms River
room_description: When Santa refused to make Malus a toymaker, Malus became determined to prove Santa wrong. So deep down in the North Pole Workshop Malus began creating toys and games in an effort to force Santa to recognize his talents. Malus realized he needed just one thing to get Santa's attention. Can you find out what it is before it's too late, save Christmas and help Malus achieve his dream of becoming a toymaker?
